text: Ingleburn may refer to: *Ingleburn, New South Wales a place in Australia. *Tetbury Avon, a river in England, known locally as the Ingleburn. *Ingleburne, McLaren Vale, South Australia a historic farming property (1851-1998). *Ingleburne, McLaren Vale, South Australia an 1850s stone building with two storeys and a Georgian facade, originally the homestead for the historic farming property (1851-1998) of the same name.
title: Ingleburn
